text: Ahmed Amine Galdoune (born 31 May 1996) is a Moroccan cyclist, who currently rides for UCI Continental team . ==Major results== ;2014 :1st 20px Time trial, National Junior Road Championships ;2016 :1st Stage 2 Tour de Hongrie : African Track Championships ::1st Keirin ::3rd Points race ;2017 :1st GP Sakia El Hamra, Les Challenges de la Marche Verte : Challenge du Prince ::1st Trophée de la Maison Royale ::2nd Trophée de l'Anniversaire :3rd Road race, African Road Championships ==References== ==External links== * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Moroccan male cyclists
